content: Had to buy it, too good, one thing... Please add option to hide Premium Key app
Absolutely fantastic! A helluva Drum synth, with great fx!
Bought the key, still had ads.
replyContent: 1. Update G-Stomper Rhythm to the latest version. 2. Please restart G-Stomper Rhythm (as clearly advised in the key description). In the G-Stomper Rhythm app, press exit, then discard and exit. Then start the app again, and the ads are gone.

content: I used to play with Rebirth and Fruity Loops back around '99-01. Fruity Loops kept expanding, eventually got bought out by Cakewalk and turned into a whole big studio production thing. That's not what I need. I need a basic sequencer I can rough out ideas on to play guitar with. This did exactly what I wanted with a clean, professional looking interface that was easy to figure out. I gladly paid for the premium version. More sample packs with premium key would be nice.
so you must restart of it doesnt work ... restart the gstomper then it should work
replyContent:
Yes, you must, as clearly stated in the app description of the key, restart G-Stomper Rhythm activate the key.
--Once the key is installed, RESTART G-Stomper Rhythm and it'll come up without advertisements.--
